/* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   day / night — but as an absurd, multi-act celestial cinematic.
   one click and the sun sets, the sky bleeds through sunset into night,
   stars ignite, a constellation draws itself, shooting stars streak, an
   aurora breathes, the moon climbs — then the freshly-themed page is
   revealed through an aperture that irises out of the toggle button.
